-- Economy Minister Bruederle to Stand in for Schaeuble at G-20, DPA Reports
-- B y   B r i a n   P a r k i n
-- 2010-10-05T15:46:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/economy-minister-bruederle-to-stand-in-for-schaeuble-at-g-20-dpa-reports.html
German Economy Minister Rainer
Bruederle will stand in for his ill colleague, Wolfgang
Schaeuble, at a meeting of Group of 20 finance ministers in
South Korea this month, Deutsche Presse-Agentur reported, citing
unnamed government sources.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Parkin in Berlin at 
 bparkin@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
